summary: A house lies ahead, just make your way through the Nordic ruin.
descriptionHtml: Originally began as a home with a mining operation in the mountain behind Riverwood. While mining, a Nordic ruin was uncovered. This uncovering led to an excavation for valuables; however, it proved unwise as the miners were constantly fighting draugers. In the end, the operation was abandoned and the owner left Skyrim leaving an note on the front door. Care to read it?
author: Stevo_the_gamer
